value.string: This metabot will send an email if the bot fails
Value set in v2 of the framework for the vLogFilePath
Replace "Error Message:" if already exists in the var
1. Send email to Service Now to create the incident - sending to trinet@service-now.com - and alert the Email_ToRecipients that the bot failed
Version 2 of the framework. Includes attachment of the csv log file.

value.expression:
$s-i-BotName$ failure on $m-date-string$ on computer $m-string-1$ (RPA)

Error Message: $s-i-ErrorMessage$

Please refer to the incident created for the failure.

Thank you and have a great day!
